                Hic requiescit in pace <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>onae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> Candidianus <lb n="3"/>p<expan><ex>res</ex><abbr>b</abbr><ex>yte</ex><abbr>r</abbr></expan> qui vixit in s<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>colum <note>sic</note> annus <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>pl</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> XL <lb n="5"/>et in presbiteratum <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>habuit annus <note>sic</note> XI
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 4: p(lus). Im freien unteren Drittel des Inschriftenfeldes befinden sich senkrecht zur oberen Inschrift vier neuzeitlich eingemeißelte Zeilen.</p>
            </div>
